headline: Should You Buy Walmart Stock? This Dow Jones Stock Could Offer Better Value for 2025
summary: Walmart (NYSE: WMT) stock has had an incredible run over the last few years.  Walmart shares have trounced the Dow Jones Industrial Average (DJINDICES: ^DJI), which has returned 35%.  There hasn't been a noticeable change in the company's growth trajectory.
